race.description: The Lids Fly Hosted Pots 5Th Grade F
race.comment: BUSH BOUQUET (3) goes very well over this track and trip including three wins. Comes off a (21.57) win last time, scoring by 1.75 lengths in a Grade 5 over 390m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. BEXLEY (1) has a strong record this journey with five wins and a minor from nine starts. Scored by 0.8 lengths last time (21.82) in a Grade 5 over 390m at this track. Looks suited here and can measure up. IDEA'S GIRL (4) is progressing well scoring last time out (21.62) at this track and bringing up her 12th career win. Form here is sound including two wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from six starts. Must be included in calculations. CASH HANDY (2) has won at this course and distance so worth considering.
